Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:02.43,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Now port de bras.{note: port de bras is a position to assume in dancing}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.83,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:08.47,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Like you're sliding against the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.00,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:16.28,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Madoka, you're not feeling the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.75,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Feel the energy, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.88,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:25.45,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}My parents are normal people, so obviously that isn't my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:31.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though, I guess my name isn't that important. We'll just skip over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.90,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}One month ago I was found unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:40.74,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then, I've been living at her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.21,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is an elite Tokyo University graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:50.71,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}but her ex-boyfriend was jealous of her accomplishments and cheated on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:01:01.09,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now she'll only date more successful men, tall guys with lots of money and fancy degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi… senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.76,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:12.83,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm shorter than her and I don't have any money, but even so she's very kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:15.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, sex is not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:20.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? Because I'm just her pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.34,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nice to see you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.85,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,He looks very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So much that it annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.29,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hey, how long are you going to let him stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.52,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,What does this kid do during the day anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Apparently he's been going to dance lessons lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.96,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you're letting him eat for free, you should make him do some chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, I tried. But whatever it was, it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:48.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,When I make him cook, he cuts his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If I make him clean up after himself, he breaks my Ginori plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Once I made him dry the futons, and he dropped them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The landlord was furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:55.78,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:02:00.62,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Forget about him and listen. Hasumi-senpai is back in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Do you remember him? Back when I was still training to be a journalist in Kofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.29,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Umm, this concerns me more than your senior classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,This? Don't worry about it. I'm talking about my senpai here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:12.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's even hotter than he was four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.90,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,So you think the unrequited love from four years ago will respark?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I even found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.94,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, this is from Kofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,You two look cute together height-wise,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,like a couple of friendly archaeologists too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,We were in the middle of research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.78,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Did you meet and talk with him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.68,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I met him, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi… senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.25,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya… right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:43.56,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Long time no see. It's been what, four years?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh no, I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And my womanly pride got in the way again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.38,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, I figured it was your expressionless face. Like a Noh-mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't say Noh-mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.05,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk to him some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wanted to, but you know I'm lousy at small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And it was so unexpected. I was worried about my makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wasn't prepared, so I didn't want him to see me acting like an idiot.\NNot after having been apart for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.10,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,See, you care too much about showing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.63,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,That part of you is really unattractive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.40,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm going to tell you straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Men prefer their girls ditzy and giggly to cool and successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:33.98,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Men prefer their girls ditzy and giggly to cool and successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.88,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,Because it's a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's why I don't like men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:55.63,title,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Kimi wa petto\NYou are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.63,episode,text,0,0,0,,[sign]2. A pet's effect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.17,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, Miyamoto-san! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.67,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh Takenouchi-san, let's cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.75,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't park here—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.89,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the new resident in 106! Was today your move-in date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.59,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm under your care now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.76,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.59,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Should we back up the truck some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.20,petto,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.13,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Please back up the truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:32.53,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.42,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Something hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:54.26,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sumire-chan! Hey, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you even in here?\NI told you to stay out of my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.59,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because I'm so hungry…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.37,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But if you're not going to make me any breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.87,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'll just sleep here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Like I'd let you…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So annoying…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I could've slept in till around two today. It's a late day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was only asleep for three hours. Why did I have to get up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't put in any eggs. I think I'm developing an allergy to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.62,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,How long are you planning on staying anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.42,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hmm… until you tell me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Next time you wake me up, I'll stuff you in a box and throw you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.90,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Here. Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:37.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.97,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I have a performance on the next holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.97,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Performance? Oh, your dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Will you come see it? I'm going to dance a solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's neat, that you do this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hey, which name's yours, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, this person's name is Goda Takeshi. Isn't that the same name as Jaian?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.85,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nevermind the names. So can you come, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll have the day off or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,So you're not going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't help it, I have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's hectic as it is because I just got transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I couldn't get by if I had to fulfill your every wish at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.03,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Aw man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:10.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're lucky, pets can be so carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're not doing anything useful, so please don't ask to be spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.87,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Am I really that useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yep, useless. I didn't know that kids these days were so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You can't even properly carry the futons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:25.18,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, then if I can do sit-ups, will you come see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:25.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.92,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay, I don't expect much from you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:31.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm just grateful you can take care of your own waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.06,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,The pose of repentance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.29,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I saw it at Nikkou the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I apologized, didn't I? So will you come see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:49.00,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, see? I can even spin plates! Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't break it! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.80,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:57.10,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:57.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, my Ginori plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.61,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's why I love you, Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:00.62,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,SIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.48,signs,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Tokyo Newspaper Company
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.89,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Oh! That's him. The new guy, Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.66,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Are you serious? That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.79,petto,girl,0,0,0,,He's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.13,petto,girl,0,0,0,,I heard he's an elite coming from Rio de Janeiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.50,petto,girl,0,0,0,,and that he's even gotten an award from the Journalists Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.63,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Didn't he personally interview Brazil's president?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.00,petto,girl,0,0,0,,You're so lucky, Kuraki. You get to work in the same office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.20,petto overlap,girl,0,0,0,,[something missing here?]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.58,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I was starting to consider any single elite journalist,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.98,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,even if they were a bit ugly,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.71,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,but now…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.71,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.78,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.25,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.89,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,He's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.59,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I've got to go for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:47.50,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.20,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.90,petto,girl,0,0,0,,You're so silly, Fukushima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.80,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Here is your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.12,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.26,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Tanaka knows the Social department inside and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:19.29,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Perhaps we can get information from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:25.57,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Oh and starting next month, we'll be working on a special project.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.10,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The first week will be…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.84,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.87,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The first week will be on infertility, and it'll run over the next five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.04,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The members will be…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:40.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why can't I be cute like that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:46.06,signs,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Four years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.96,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming, even though you had your own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh it's all right, I wasn't that busy or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:52.93,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.70,petto overlap,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.50,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:13.42,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Not at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.95,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hey, let's take a picture for the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.26,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll take it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.08,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Excuse me, would you mind taking a picture for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.05,petto,man,0,0,0,,Oh, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.55,petto,man,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.79,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:56.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time, too, I couldn't be true to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. My dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:07.47,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Wow, a female journalist in a hands-on research?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.97,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The diet project we did last time like that also was effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:13.80,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,That Chemistry department journalist\Nis apparently your colleague, Iwaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.81,0:10:15.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.28,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,It was very good research,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:19.81,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,but a smart person like you could probably write something even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.52,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.49,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,In the weekly, doing hands-on research on four mascot shows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.79,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san in an animal suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:31.50,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Yes. This spring the Tokyo Familyland we sponsor is having
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.33,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,a grand reopening, and we've been asked to write about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.50,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,This show is apparently especially popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.07,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to reading your work, Iwaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:43.34,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The destiny of the Lifestyle department is in your elite journalistic hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.11,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Iwaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why do I have to dress in an animal suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:54.55,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.62,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.76,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Your forehead is wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:13.34,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,When you're tired, try imagining yourself stranded on an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:14.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.04,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Close your eyes and picture a blue sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.38,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I really don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's that? A malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:32.35,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,And now you must live all by yourself on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.79,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You're lonely, there's no sign of civilization, and the night is pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.23,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,At times like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:43.06,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,if you could've brought just one item with you, what would you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is this some form of counseling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.70,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,No, just a personal question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then excuse me, but I don't have time to talk right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,or to waste on pointless fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.74,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,If I were you, I would bring along my dog, Maron-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.75,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What, a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:04.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You'd want the kinds of things that can help in emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.79,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,That's right. It's just like you to think that way, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that Chihuahua going to be of some use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.33,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes. He's seen me through times of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Times of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:21.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder what I would bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:26.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe a phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.58,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.68,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I will need fire, so maybe a lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.51,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:35.22,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,You are a good person, Iwaya-san. Pretty, smart and responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.69,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What, it's moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait a second, did you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.13,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Next time, let's talk on the fourteenth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:47.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's enough, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not so weak as to always have to depend on a counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:56.04,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,As you say, today's women have become stronger, for good or ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.01,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,They didn't get that way on purpose though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.78,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,It just happened because they worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.08,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,Once you have figured out an answer, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.75,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,What is most important to you as you try to survive on that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Umm—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:21.00,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,In this world, everyone is stranded on their own island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.14,petto,counsel,0,0,0,,I have discovered an oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.61,petto,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.55,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,What? You've become a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.38,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yup, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:42.05,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Pets get a place to stay and food for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.25,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Plus my owner is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.49,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,So basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.05,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,you're a gigolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.03,petto overlap,Takeshi,0,0,0,,No, not a gigolo. Just a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:52.06,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,What? I don't get it. What do you mean by pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.83,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hmm… kinda like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:56.53,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.97,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah. Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.90,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Watching them revitalizes the spirit. That's how I am for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.34,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You say that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.44,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,I bet you've gotten laid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.94,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Nope, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.41,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You guys haven't done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.31,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,No, we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:09.04,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Last time I just peeked at her while she was in the bathtub and I got a bloody nose for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:09.94,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,She's actually pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:15.85,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But if I get kicked out, I have nowhere to go. So I'm playing nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.85,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Who are you playing nice with, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.62,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I have a new dance move, will you try it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.33,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.83,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Can I have a minute? Everyone, gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:31.53,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,So, is that master the reason you've been trying extra hard lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.34,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Me? Trying extra hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.57,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,You beat me to that role for the upcoming performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.74,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.96,petto,woman,0,0,0,,These are our image characters, Toto and Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.86,petto,woman,0,0,0,,By the way, how tall are you, Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm a little over 170 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:12.54,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Oh, you're pretty big. I guess there's only that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:16.58,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Hey, Koike-kun, could you bring that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.38,petto,man,0,0,0,,That one? All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.09,petto,man,0,0,0,,This is Toto's friend, Kumango-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.79,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,The eyes are all crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.23,petto,woman,0,0,0,,As you can see, it's kind of a silly, klutzy character.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait, do you mean that this is for…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:44.54,petto,woman,0,0,0,,Well, we can't put you in the show right away, so let's have you walk around the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:58.02,petto,man,0,0,0,,When you are wearing the costume, please move around constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:00.66,petto,man,0,0,0,,If you stand still, you'll just look like a standing decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.43,petto,man,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.67,petto,man,0,0,0,,Not just your hands, move your whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.57,petto,man,0,0,0,,You should exaggerate your actions, or you won't look like you're moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.84,petto,man,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.45,petto,boy,0,0,0,,Look, he tripped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:36.26,petto,boy,0,0,0,,Are you dumb? You're so boring, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.79,petto,boy,0,0,0,,STUPID!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.66,petto,boy,0,0,0,,We know there's a human in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.60,petto,boy,0,0,0,,Let's take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.83,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, there's a human in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:49.30,petto,boy,0,0,0,,On three. One… two…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:48.44,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}An elite Tokyo University graduate career woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:53.64,petto,man,0,0,0,,Oh no, boys! Don't you feel sorry for Kumango-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.08,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:03.45,petto,boy,0,0,0,,Run!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.62,petto,man,0,0,0,,Wait, Kumango-kun! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.13,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:14.73,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.36,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Just now, on TV…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:22.00,petto,man,0,0,0,,The parade is on everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:27.44,petto,man,0,0,0,,So let's everyone go to Tokyo Familyland!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.48,petto,man,0,0,0,,Grand reopening during Golden Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:33.85,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.05,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nothing, I just wanted to change the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.69,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I was just watching "Detective School Q"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What, got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I want to know what's going on in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I need to hear the news. I'm a journalist, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.60,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.77,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nevermind. My hip hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.71,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What happened to your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.23,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, I just tripped during my lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.25,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Did you go to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,No. I don't have my insurance papers with me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the money, what if a bone is broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.32,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, if you say you'll go with me, maybe I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.39,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't suck up to me, you know I'm busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just the hospital, go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.49,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Man, that's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:22.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You and I walking together out in the open is weird in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's the age difference, plus I'm taller than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.74,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't like having to worry about what people are thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:28.17,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Why don't you just tell them? Say that I'm your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.31,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you joking? Just make sure you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:51.14,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Just make sure you move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.74,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This is going to be a big scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:38.91,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.46,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,This is the best, Iwaya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.40,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,The part about how you felt like you'd pass out from the lack of oxygen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.07,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,makes the reader feel like they're right there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:09.07,petto,Ishida,0,0,0,,Wow, I didn't know you couldn't\Nget on your feet on your own in those costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.27,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Only an elite like you could
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.47,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,make a boring subject like this sound so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:16.01,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,How about it? For this afternoon's parade,\Nwe can have the Photography department go along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:18.45,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,That sounds great! We could take up more space for the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.32,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Why don't we stick Iwaya-san's picture and profile in there as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.08,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Good, good. If we stick a picture with her looking her usual
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:26.45,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,indifferent self next to the one of her in the costume…\NKind of like a before and after—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.02,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't think that will be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.92,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just wrote the article according to the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:34.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you plan on featuring it any more than it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:37.07,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,please specifically tell me the advantages of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If there are none, that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.31,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Umm, it was just a light joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not accustomed to hearing jokes at my workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.12,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:57.39,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,What a boring woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.39,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I just wanted to ask you something about a project you've previously worked on, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.39,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,you seem a little busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.76,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Hasumi-kun? How is External Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.43,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, hello. It's definitely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.77,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Here, there are no incidents like the demonstrations in Venezuela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.17,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm still feeling my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:17.67,petto,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, your work has been centered on South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:19.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I understand that, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.55,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I need to learn to think more on the global level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.35,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,"Global level."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.78,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,Well, well, an expert journalist from South America definitely has a broad view.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:30.85,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Yeah, that global whatever sounds like a good word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:37.19,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I didn't know, but we kind of transferred in and out at the same time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, due to the circumstances…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:42.70,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I heard. It must've been a pretty hard punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.03,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.37,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Sorry, that didn't come out right…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:11.26,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:14.30,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.63,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I can see the patch on your hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.90,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,They make you wear an animal costume as soon as you've transferred, it's no surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I've been learning a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:26.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Everything can be chalked up as an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.98,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Do you really think that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:33.58,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is just bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:35.88,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:38.22,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,As soon as talk about your transfer came up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:40.79,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,the English newspaper department asked for you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:41.66,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.69,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,But for some reason, they stuck you in our department.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:47.33,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,They purposely threw you in a dead end position.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:50.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,How come you know all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:52.67,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I just have very good hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:54.75,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I also heard today from the External Affairs department
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:56.81,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,that they're going to have a celebration for Hasumi-san's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.14,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I think I will go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:04.98,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Men are really afraid of women getting more powerful than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:08.98,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,If you want to have things go your way, it's more advantageous to act dumb and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:14.99,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose that would be too embarrassing for a Tokyo University graduate like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:28.00,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is just bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:34.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew, I just pretended not to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:48.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've just been doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:51.56,petto,boss2,0,0,0,,You're not very good at being a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:54.56,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,They purposely put you in a place where you couldn't advance your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:24:00.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've earned everything with my own hands, from my university to my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:04.51,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,If you want to have things go your way, it's more advantageous to act dumb and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:07.18,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they saying all that effort was for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.00,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:10.51,petto,Yuri,0,0,0,,See, you tried to show off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:13.00,petto,boss_2,0,0,0,,You're really a boring woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:15.82,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.08,0:24:44.82,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm such a weak person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.02,0:24:46.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:50.75,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I came home in a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:55.96,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:57.19,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I didn't want anyone to see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:25:00.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're kidding! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.94,0:25:17.40,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't laugh at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.91,0:25:18.45,petto overlap,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.91,0:25:22.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.02,0:25:29.29,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:39.80,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't you laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.28,0:25:50.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.28,0:25:54.45,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're always so cool, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.02,0:25:57.82,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're a good cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.02,0:26:02.99,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,you're hardworking and you're always doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.30,0:26:09.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:12.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.60,0:26:16.84,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You look pretty again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.06,0:26:37.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.13,0:26:42.96,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.47,0:26:51.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.69,0:27:07.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.79,0:27:11.16,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.46,0:27:13.23,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:21.40,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can take you to an abandoned island, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.07,0:27:23.37,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,An abandoned island?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.71,0:27:27.88,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,If I have you with me, it'll probably be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.02,0:27:40.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shoot, where did I put my cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.32,0:27:44.56,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Ah man, how boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.20,0:27:48.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.56,0:27:53.74,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Hasumi from External Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.57,0:27:58.47,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you so late. Is this time okay for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.87,0:28:00.44,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, are you still at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:02.28,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Did you call to consult me about that project you're working on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:05.98,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no. That's not a problem anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.98,0:28:14.09,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I just wanted to apologize for earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.49,0:28:17.36,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about that. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.86,0:28:20.26,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.40,0:28:23.97,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's just that you stormed out, so I kind of panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.53,0:28:26.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not at all, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.47,0:28:31.61,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I just got some tickets to a Noh performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:33.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Noh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.44,0:28:38.81,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's for tomorrow at noon. Do you think you could go?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.15,0:28:40.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:45.95,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,To put it bluntly, I'm asking you on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.43,0:28:54.23,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.93,0:28:56.53,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:29:02.27,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,So tomorrow, at 1 pm, at Ginza Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.67,0:29:05.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.56,0:29:25.63,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.70,0:29:33.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.17,0:29:34.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.94,0:29:38.61,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I can't go to the hospital with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.24,0:29:42.54,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay. I had some stuff to do tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.54,0:29:42.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.91,0:29:43.61,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.25,0:29:44.85,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:47.08,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's okay, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.22,0:29:48.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,We can go the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.78,0:29:51.25,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.25,0:29:53.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.49,0:29:58.23,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Forget about it. I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.23,0:30:00.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, it completely slipped my mind. I wonder if there's anything left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.73,0:30:03.30,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What? Make something quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:04.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll make it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.61,0:30:18.65,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Should it have been shorter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.08,0:30:22.35,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't want him to thing I was trying too hard to look young.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.83,0:30:32.56,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.63,0:30:42.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,We still have about half an hour. Would you like to get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.87,0:30:43.91,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.29,0:31:02.32,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.46,0:31:05.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.16,0:31:07.76,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.76,0:31:11.50,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san and Hasumi-san? Wow, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.50,0:31:12.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.70,0:31:18.61,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Fukushima-san gave me the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.11,0:31:20.48,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.78,0:31:27.52,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Wait a second, are you two going out or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.52,0:31:29.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh no, nothing of that sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.65,0:31:29.78,petto overlap,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.98,0:31:33.09,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,He just came back to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:36.96,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Why would such a great guy like Hasumi-san have to find a girl so quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.06,0:31:38.76,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's not quite like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.86,0:31:41.60,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san's just an old friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:45.20,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I hoped you would ask me to come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.70,0:31:47.07,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.34,0:31:48.94,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I didn't notice that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.94,0:31:50.27,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Let's go, the four of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.27,0:31:52.01,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,We have tickets too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.01,0:31:53.51,petto,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Our seats are right next to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.51,0:31:55.88,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm so happy! I get to sit with Hasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:31:58.68,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Yeah, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.22,0:32:08.92,petto,man,0,0,0,,A heavy battle between the pro-wrestlers…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.92,0:32:12.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this situation, if I had to choose, I'd rather go see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:16.30,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Must-see fight?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.80,0:32:19.33,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a grammatical mistake…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.90,0:32:23.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because they're sloppy with things like that, pro-wrestling fans are looked down on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.77,0:32:24.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:29.14,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.55,0:32:35.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I have a performance on the next holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.58,0:32:39.02,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Will you come see it? I'm going to dance a solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.89,0:32:44.09,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Damn. It's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:49.46,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I was talking about going to the hospital when the performance was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.73,0:32:50.77,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.17,0:32:52.83,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm, I… My pet…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.97,0:32:53.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.47,0:32:55.90,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,My pet got injured…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.90,0:32:59.11,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He can't go to the hospital by himself and umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.14,0:33:00.14,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I've got to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.24,0:33:02.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm going home! Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.41,0:33:04.25,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm really very sorry, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.15,0:33:08.35,petto,Kuraki,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.44,0:33:30.07,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Are you really going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.51,0:33:31.87,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.07,0:33:33.14,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.38,0:33:34.98,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,You're really going to be able to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:36.61,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I'm depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:39.08,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.25,0:33:44.45,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I'm going to go make sure Junpei knows the B part well.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.89,0:33:45.52,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.25,0:33:47.19,petto,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.89,0:33:55.73,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Nobody is allowed back here before the performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.60,0:33:57.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,There you are, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.43,0:34:00.94,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.57,0:34:05.11,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.51,0:34:07.24,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.41,0:34:10.11,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You had a date, didn't you? With a guy from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.55,0:34:12.21,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.21,0:34:14.45,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't know, I could just tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.52,0:34:19.59,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you tell me that tonight was your performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.75,0:34:22.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Because you looked so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.76,0:34:28.20,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Who you choose to spend your time with is up to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.33,0:34:31.90,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,but when you lied, it pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.21,0:34:41.04,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You didn't go to the hospital, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.98,0:34:42.68,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.71,0:34:46.58,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,But they took out some of the jumps and lifts so it shouldn't be too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.22,0:34:51.39,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,And I have to take the responsibility, since I'm the one who injured it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.86,0:34:55.86,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.66,0:34:57.49,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.40,0:35:01.26,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.00,0:35:03.00,petto,Junpei,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:14.91,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Pay for the ticket to see my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.61,0:35:19.78,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.07,0:35:39.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo. His real name is Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.65,0:38:07.82,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.69,0:38:13.46,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work! You looked so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.46,0:38:14.16,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:19.33,petto,girl,0,0,0,,You're really the best. Please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.33,0:38:21.26,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't have to. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.75,0:38:43.85,petto,girl,0,0,0,,Great job! May I shake your hand? Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.65,0:38:48.46,petto,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thank you, I wonder what's inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.49,0:38:51.49,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,He almost seems like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.44,0:39:09.51,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.75,0:39:21.89,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,They told me to refrain from too much strenuous activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.19,0:39:23.59,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Can you bathe me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.16,0:39:25.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.90,0:39:28.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,After your bath, I'll put some ice on your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.57,0:39:33.07,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,That's thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.67,0:39:36.27,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.01,0:39:39.51,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,You were the best out of all of them, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.88,0:39:41.94,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:44.01,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup, I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.85,0:39:49.92,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,It would have been even better if I hadn't been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.39,0:39:55.46,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey. You're not going to scold me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.76,0:39:57.43,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You don't like being seen like this in public, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.23,0:40:07.50,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wish I could have given you a big bouquet of flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.75,0:40:21.58,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Okay, time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.02,0:40:24.79,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,All right, let's go home. Sumire-chan, gimme a piggyback ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.79,0:40:25.72,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.06,0:40:29.12,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.06,0:40:30.93,petto,Momo,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.73,0:40:34.23,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That was a good movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.50,0:40:35.15,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.10,0:40:38.37,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.87,0:40:40.97,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's fine, you really don't have to apologize so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.30,0:40:44.04,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, but I have to apologize myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.04,0:40:44.57,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.11,0:40:48.81,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,People have been calling you a Noh mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.81,0:40:49.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.98,0:40:53.21,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukushima-san and her friend told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.48,0:40:57.02,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it was an inconsiderate choice for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.02,0:40:57.99,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.22,0:41:01.76,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I like them! I really do, Noh masks and kokeshi dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.13,0:41:11.77,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Some things about you haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.47,0:41:18.67,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,To tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.51,0:41:21.68,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,when I first met you in the elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.08,0:41:23.45,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.85,0:41:27.32,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You had become so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.95,0:41:30.05,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.99,0:41:32.59,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Inside, you're still the same as back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.66,0:41:38.99,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're smart, but afraid to be yourself. Hardworking, but clumsy…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.00,0:41:42.20,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.20,0:41:43.06,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yes, that's how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.57,0:41:46.17,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, and remember that last day in Kofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.53,0:41:48.57,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,When I told you we should take a picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.17,0:41:53.04,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,you said "yes" and tried to take it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.51,0:41:56.88,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I laugh every time I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.55,0:41:58.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.85,0:42:02.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The way you always apologize hasn't changed, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.66,0:42:09.89,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.99,0:42:13.80,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.50,0:42:19.37,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,when you came to see me off in your work clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.34,0:42:24.61,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I dunno, I just felt really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.64,0:42:29.98,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's kinda late, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.52,0:42:39.55,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.36,0:42:47.10,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm also… very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.03,0:42:50.73,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't put it into words well, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.17,0:42:56.00,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you invited me to the Noh performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.64,0:42:58.81,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,and the way we can walk together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.55,0:43:06.78,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'll walk you back to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.32,0:43:10.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.52,0:43:16.32,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.03,0:43:17.63,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,home?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.23,0:43:28.94,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow, so you live here?|this is where you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.94,0:43:30.64,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.64,0:43:31.34,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.34,0:43:32.87,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, here is fine for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.91,0:43:34.00,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san from the fourth floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.08,0:43:34.41,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.74,0:43:39.58,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,You dropped your futon blankets again! Please don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:41.35,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll help carry them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.28,0:43:44.85,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.59,0:43:47.90,petto,landlord,0,0,0,,Please be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.96,0:43:48.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.56,0:43:56.20,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You were drying quite a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.85,0:43:57.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.27,0:44:00.70,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I'm sorry, I had many guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.17,0:44:04.84,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Here is fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.97,0:44:06.94,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, I can bring them to your front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.04,0:44:08.14,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.02,0:44:24.56,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.09,0:44:27.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really, you were a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.99,0:44:29.93,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,So, that's it. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.84,0:44:40.18,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What I've really been trying to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:45.45,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All day, really, is that…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.42,0:44:51.99,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Since you came to see me off, four years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.72,0:44:56.69,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, from even before that…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.69,0:45:00.00,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.90,0:45:03.37,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was with you all this time, but I couldn't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.23,0:45:05.70,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I tried to forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.63,0:45:07.70,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.40,0:45:09.57,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Coming back…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.11,0:45:11.74,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And meeting you again after four years…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.84,0:45:12.91,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The moment I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.91,0:45:17.95,petto,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I just felt like I had to make you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.08,0:45:22.52,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpa—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.18,0:45:52.78,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.62,0:45:57.95,petto,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, be quiet!
